      "id": "PopularPost102838",
      "post_content": "It's not [Wildfire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wildfire)  \nWildfire made each player sacrifice land. This destroys it.  \nWildfire affected every player, this is only one target other player.  \nnormally this doesn't matter, but if you're playing a group game or your opponent has [Darksteel Citadel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darksteel Citadel)s then this is strictly worse.",
